  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'After your hovercraft crashes on a volcanic planet, your aircraft-spaceship
    hybrid is damaged. Only the hot-air balloon module remains attached to your vehicle,
    giving you a way to navigate the hazardous terrain.


    To survive, you must
    complete two challenges. First, collect the key scattered across the volcanic
    map to unlock the repair house. Second, reach 500 altitude by carefully manipulating
    the heat in the balloon. Increasing heat allows you to rise, while reducing heat
    lets you descend, using thermodynamics to stay safe.


    Mastering both collecting
    the key and controlling altitude tests your skill and understanding of heat and
    gas mechanics.


    By completing these tasks, you reach the repair station,
    fix your vehicle, and prepare to return home, triumphant after your adventure
    in ATLAS'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
