  m_text: "You\u2019ve crash-landed in the mysterious world of ATLAS, a place filled
    with physics, hidden technology, and challenges. Your only way out is to rebuild
    your damaged vehicle from scratch and uncover the secrets this world holds.\n\nBeside
    you is Gizmo, your loyal droid companion. Together, you\u2019ll explore and face
    different adventures, learning the principles of physics needed to repair and
    improve your vehicle. Gizmo will guide you through every challenge. \n\nEach
    step brings new discoveries and tests your understanding of how the world works.
    By learning physics concepts and applying them to real challenges, you\u2019ll
    transform broken pieces into a powerful vehicle that can adapt to any terrain.\n\nBut
    Atlas is more than just a place to escape  it\u2019s a world built to make you
    think, create, and grow. Only by completing your vehicle and overcoming every
    challenge can you finally rise beyond the map of Atlas."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -4890204404628985631, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
