  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "After fixing the balance in the sky, you rise higher and reach space.
    At first, everything is calm, and the hover moves smoothly among the stars. But
    soon, a meteor storm appears. Rocks fly past the hover, shaking it and pushing
    it off course.\n\nYou hold the controls tightly and focus on every movement.
    By turning carefully, you dodge the flying rocks and keep the hover steady. Each
    correct move helps you avoid collisions and slowly regain control. The meteors
    continue to fall, but you stay calm and use what you\u2019ve learned to navigate
    safely through the storm.\n\nFinally, you escape the meteor field and enter calm
    space again. The hover flies straight, smooth, and steady. The danger is gone.
    Gizmo praises you for steering through the storm and keeping the hover safe.
    You realize that by controlling the hover carefully, you can handle even the
    toughest challenges in space. With your new skills, you are ready for the next
    part of your journey, confident that you can face any danger ahead."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -4890204404628985631, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
