  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'You and Gizmo arrive at a sci-fi power plant where the hovercraft has
    very low power because of the recent activity which is the First Test and Racing
    with Newton. It cannot rise into the air, and its power core is too weak to run
    the hover. Nothing is working, and the power system is completely unstable. You
    learn that the problem is connected to work, energy, and power. Work happens
    when a force makes something move, and energy is needed for that movement to
    happen.


    Your job is to push the red energy source into the white storage
    box before the timer runs out. When you push the power cell, you are doing work,
    and this sends energy back to the hovercraft. You must move quickly and stay
    focused, because if you fail, the hover will shut down. While restoring the power,
    you also learn that power shows how fast energy is used.


    When the energy
    starts flowing again, the engines return to life. With the power system fixed,
    the hovercraft becomes ready to lift off again.

'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -4890204404628985631, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
