  m_text: 'After completing your last challenge in space, you return to the ATLAS
    map to choose your next adventure. Now that you have learned to control the hover,
    it is time to continue exploring the universe. Your hover rises smoothly, leaving
    the space station behind and moving deeper into the vastness of space. Stars
    shine all around, and the journey feels exciting and new.


    The flight is
    calm, giving you time to enjoy the view and prepare for what lies ahead. As you
    travel, you guide the hover carefully, making small adjustments to stay on course.
    You practice steering through space, using everything you learned from the previous
    challenges to navigate safely.


    After traveling through the endless darkness
    of space, you finally arrive at the next destination, a space station. Your hover
    lands safely, and you step inside, ready for the next mission.'
